sentence: IDF  says  20  killed  in  al-Shifa  hospital  raid.

article_title: IDF says 20 killed in al-Shifa hospital raid.
sentence: Twenty  people,  who  the  IDF  describe  as  "terrorists",  have  been  killed  and  "dozens  of  apprehended  suspects  are  currently  in  questioning",  the  statement  says.
